tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: 100% satisfaction!! Prompt hygienic treatment. Proper explanation of diagnosis, and aftercare. 👍👍👍👍

Doctor Khaiwan provides fantastic service. He not only performs the procedure with almost no pain but he also explains the problems in simple manner for patients to understand. He was able to identify the issue with my teeth in one sitting while other doctor i visited could not identify the issue. I would highly recommend him.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
For some one who is petrified of dentists, the notion stands changed after visiting Dr. Shroff. He is a very patient doctor with thorough professionalism. I am extremely happy with my visit to Dr. Shroff’s clinic and I would highly highly recommend this place for anyone with dental issues.
Thank You Dr. Shroff.
